languages.text: "Мои собратья не смогли найти это место. Темные кузены... едва ли могли ограничиться одним трофеем, пусть и подобных масштабов. Нет. Здесь действовали грубо и быстро — поведение, скорее присущее мон-кай".

"My kin were unable to find this place. The Dark Ones... would hardly have been content with a single trophy, even one as great as this. No. This was done crudely and quickly — behaviour more typical of mon-keigh."

languages.text: “我的族人没能找到这个地方。至于那些黑暗子嗣……就算他们真的夺走了那件珍贵的战利品，也绝不会抢完之后立刻收手。不，这场破坏非常粗暴、非常迅速，更像是猴子的典型行为。”
languages.original_text: "My kin were unable to find this place. The Dark Ones... would hardly have been content with a single trophy, even one as great as this. No. This was done crudely and quickly — behaviour more typical of mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: “我的族人没能找到这个地方。至于我那些黑暗的亲族……就算他们真的夺走了那件珍贵的战利品，也绝不会夺走它之后好奇立刻收手。不，这场破坏非常粗暴、非常迅速，更像是猴子的典型行为。”
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Mein Volk konnte dieses Versteck nicht finden. Die Dunklen ... hätten sich wohl kaum mit einer einzigen Trophäe zufriedengegeben, selbst wenn sie noch so gewaltig ist. Nein. Das ging grob und schnell über die Bühne, und ein solches Verhalten ist eher typisch für die Chem-Pan-Sey."
languages.original_text: "My kin were unable to find this place. The Dark Ones... would hardly have been content with a single trophy, even one as great as this. No. This was done crudely and quickly — behaviour more typical of mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: "Mein Volk konnte dieses Versteck nicht finden. Unsere dunklen Vettern ... hätten sich wohl kaum mit einer einzigen Trophäe zufriedengegeben, selbst wenn sie noch so gewaltig ist. Nein. Das ging grob und schnell über die Bühne, und ein solches Verhalten ist eher typisch für die Chem-Pan-Sey."
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: «Mis congéneres no pudieron hallar este sitio. Los oscuros... no se habrían conformado con un solo trofeo, ni siquiera uno tan grandioso como este. No, esto ha sido tosco y apresurado, y tal conducta es más típica de los mon-keigh».
languages.original_text: "My kin were unable to find this place. The Dark Ones... would hardly have been content with a single trophy, even one as great as this. No. This was done crudely and quickly — behaviour more typical of mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: «Mis congéneres no pudieron hallar este sitio. Nuestros parientes oscuros... no se habrían conformado con un solo trofeo, ni siquiera uno tan grandioso como este. No, esto ha sido tosco y apresurado, y tal conducta es más típica de los mon-keigh».
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: « Mes semblables n'ont pas réussi à trouver cet endroit. Les Drukharis... ne se seraient pas contentés d'un seul trophée, même aussi important que celui-ci. Non, ce travail est trop rapide et rudimentaire ; un comportement plus typique des mon-keigh. »
languages.original_text: "My kin were unable to find this place. The Dark Ones... would hardly have been content with a single trophy, even one as great as this. No. This was done crudely and quickly — behaviour more typical of mon-keigh."

traits.locale_text: « Mes semblables n'ont pas réussi à trouver cet endroit. Nos sombres cousins... ne se seraient pas contentés d'un seul trophée, même aussi important que celui-ci. Non, ce travail est trop rapide et rudimentaire ; un comportement plus typique des mon-keigh. »
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: 「同胞はこの場所を見つけられなかった。しかし、暗黒の者たちは…たとえこれほど偉大なものであっても、戦利品ひとつでは満足しなかっただろう。いや、これは粗雑かつ迅速に行われたものであり、その行動はむしろモン＝ケイの典型だ」
languages.original_text: "My kin were unable to find this place. The Dark Ones... would hardly have been content with a single trophy, even one as great as this. No. This was done crudely and quickly — behaviour more typical of mon-keigh."

languages.text: "Soydaşlarım burayı bulamadı. Karalar... Bunun kadar büyük olsa bile tek bir ödülle yetinmezler. Yok. Bunlar çok baştan savma, alelacele yapılmış... Mon-keigh işi olduğu her hâlinden belli."
